\toc3 2Ko
\mt1 KORIN CAPAT
\mt2 A Pabae Nah
\mt4 (Second Letter to the Corinthians)
\is2 KORIN CAPAT A PABAE KAWNG
\im Korin Khrihca hlang boel taengla Paul tlek a caeh thai pawt vaengah tah Paul te a noih uh. Te kawng te amih ham koep a thuicaih pah. Te vaengah Paul loh a lungbuei te a then ben la a hoi. (1.23). A hnukbang rhoek long khaw a uen bangla khosak sak te a ngaihnah om. A ka tholh khaw khodawk ngai tih pilnam te hloep ham a ngaih bal. (2.5—11).
\ip Pathen tah moeihoeih Pathen la a om dongah Jerusalem neh Judea kah kah hlang rhoek ham bomnah a paek uh. (8.1—-9.15). Paul tah olkhueh thai dongkah Pathen tueihyoeih la om (3.1—17). Amah te bahoeng patang dae Pathen taengla pilnam mawt ham tlungmu. (4.1—-6.13; 10.1—-12.10). He cabu he AD 57 tluk vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Paul loh Pathen Uemonah \ior (1. 1)\ior*
\io1 Pathen pilnam ham caeltueih bibi \ior (1. 12—2. 17) \ior*
\io1 Guided by the Love of Christ \ior (3. 1—7. 16)\ior*
\io1 Khodaeng bomnnah \ior (8. 1—9. 15)\ior*
\io1 Paul caeltueih taktak ni \ior (10. 1—13. 10)\ior*
\io1 Phihnah ol \ior (13. 11-13)\ior*
